cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or challenge this evidence repository, please cite as:"
type: software
title: "Voynich Manuscript Decipherment — Evidence Repository"
abstract: >
  Reproducible statistical evidence for the decipherment of Voynich Manuscript
  (Beinecke MS 408) as a pharmaceutical text in a hybrid Classical Mongolian /
  Tibetan Sowa Rigpa register, encrypted by rotational substitution cipher at R=14.
  Contains five independent pre-registered statistical tests, all passing, with full
  corpus verification scripts and negative results documentation.
authors:
